data.title: Franklin Co. Marriage Records
data.text:
FRANKLIN COUNTY MARRIAGE RECORDS AS OF FEBRUARY 8, 2001 GROOM'S LAST NAMES -- WHI - WY

To locate a marriage record, click on the Edit pull down menu, click on Find(on this page), enter the last name and it should find that name and highlight it. This list is in alphabetical order by groom's name but you can also enter the bride's last name on your search and it should find it. If you have any problems or need a copy of a license, please give our office a call at 785-242-6000.
